About

Reian Artz (ReiArtz) is all about showcasing some of Reian's artworks.


She started out as a young child, in her own world and lonely. Her drawings and her nightmares were the only things that kept her company. Refusing to let these tribulations succeed in taking over her, she started to get inspired by them. Fueled with this determination, she picked up a pen and paper, and started to work.


Additionally, she worries about the future, particularly her own memories. She started to forget small things, but overtime, they end up becoming big on its own. The first thing she thought to immortalize something important to her was through art. And she hopes that this will be the same solution for others.

"Reian"
